        "text_NDVhyq": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Traditional hand sanitizers rely on high-alcohol formulas that strip your skin's natural moisture every time you use them. Repeat use leads to dry, cracked skin — which ironically makes you more vulnerable to the very germs you're trying to avoid.</p><p>We went a different direction.</p><p>Bee Clean's patent-pending beeswax infusion works differently at the surface level. Rather than just evaporating after use, it leaves behind a thin, protective antimicrobial barrier that continues to work — while also softening and conditioning your skin. Every spray does double duty.</p><p>Our beeswax-based formulas are designed to kill germs effectively while supporting skin health, challenging the idea that “clean” has to mean harsh, drying, or chemical-heavy.</p>"
